/2024-04-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-killed-by-hezbollah-anti-tank-missile-fired-from-lebanon/0000018f-1947-d0a5-abcf-3fff64b00000</guid></item><item><title>由于担心联盟的终结，内塔尼亚胡因人质交易而倾向于拉法行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-26/ty-article/.premium/fearing-the-end-of-his-coalition-netanyahu-edges-toward-rafah-operation-over-hostage-deal/0000018f-169d-d2e1-a7df-17bf7a680000</link><description>拉法行动将危及人质，可能不会推翻哈马斯 ■ 政府支持针对人质家人的恐吓行动，但未能援助北部流离失所的人们 ■ 只要以色列袭击加沙，真主党的纳斯鲁拉就不会退缩</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 03:00:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-26/ty-article/.premium/fearing-the-end-of-his-coalition-netanyahu-edges-toward-rafah-operation-over-hostage-deal/0000018f-169d-d2e1-a7df-17bf7a680000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在拉法的行动可能决定与真主党的“信息战”是否会成为现实</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-26/ty-article/.premium/gazas-rafah-may-decide-whether-israels-war-of-messages-with-hezbollah-becomes-real/0000018f-16bb-d361-a3ef-56fb20cf0000</link><description>以色列在加沙南部城市的军事行动可能会导致总部位于黎巴嫩的组织决定是否与以色列发动大规模战争</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 03:00:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-26/ty-article/.premium/gazas-rafah-may-decide-whether-israels-war-of-messages-with-hezbollah-becomes-real/0000018f-16bb-d361-a3ef-56fb20cf0000</guid></item><item><title>报告：美国不会制裁在约旦河西岸活动的极端正统以色列国防军部队</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-26/ty-article-live/egyptian-delegation-set-to-arrive-in-israel-to-jumpstart-hostage-talks/0000018f-1835-d1f3-afcf-3b75be9b0000</link><description>美国广播公司新闻报道拜登政府在制裁 Netzah Yehuda 营问题上出现了退缩 ■ 从黎巴嫩向多夫山发射火箭，导致基础设施施工人员死亡 ■ 联合国官员称可能需要 14 年时间才能清理加沙废墟 ■ 埃及代表团抵达以色列参加人质交易谈判■ 以色列国防军称两名策划恐怖袭击的巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸被捕 ■ 白宫否认哈马斯关于政府镇压大学校园亲巴勒斯坦抗议活动的指控</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 02:37:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-26/ty-article-live/egyptian-delegation-set-to-arrive-in-israel-to-jumpstart-hostage-talks/0000018f-1835-d1f3-afcf-3b75be9b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府拨款4亿美元用于恢复加沙边境社区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-government-allocates-400-million-to-rehabilitation-of-gaza-border-communities/0000018f-16e6-d361-a3ef-56f7626a0000</link><description>以色列内阁决定将为距离加沙边境7公里以内的房屋翻修提供资金，但总理内塔尼亚胡无法顶住市长的压力，意味着更多的开发资金尚未分配</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 21:08:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-government-allocates-400-million-to-rehabilitation-of-gaza-border-communities/0000018f-16e6-d361-a3ef-56f7626a0000</guid></item><item><title>辛·贝特（Shin Bet）是犹太人救援者、被指控的纳粹合作者鲁道夫·卡兹特纳（Rudolf Kasztner）被谋杀的幕后黑手吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/was-shin-bet-behind-murder-of-rudolf-kasztner-rescuer-of-jews-alleged-nazi-collaborator/0000018f-16b6-da70-a7bf-7fbfdfc50000</link><description>为什么辛贝特仍在审查 1957 年与暗杀鲁道夫（以色列）卡斯特纳有关的文件？历史学家纳达夫·卡普兰对这起谋杀案及其离奇的调查有一个大胆的——如果不是令人震惊的——理论</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 21:05:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/was-shin-bet-behind-murder-of-rudolf-kasztner-rescuer-of-jews-alleged-nazi-collaborator/0000018f-16b6-da70-a7bf-7fbfdfc50000</guid></item><item><title>“你将拥有我的孩子”：被释放的以色列人质说哈马斯绑架者想娶她</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-25/ty-article/you-will-have-my-children-freed-israeli-hostage-says-hamas-captor-wanted-to-marry-her/0000018f-16a9-dc39-a9cf-b7ef661e0000</link><description>韦斯告诉第 12 频道新闻，她与被囚禁的母亲团聚。 “其中一名哈马斯尼克分子说他爱我，他带我母亲来是为了同意我们结婚，”她回忆道。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 20:19:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-25/ty-article/you-will-have-my-children-freed-israeli-hostage-says-hamas-captor-wanted-to-marry-her/0000018f-16a9-dc39-a9cf-b7ef661e0000</guid></item><item><tit